    "I still believe these results are very motivating for PAC-Bayes as they show that very tight bounds are possible.",
    "The numerical comparison of the various bounds in the context of deep-learning is also of interest.",
    "Other experimental comparisons of the bounds are available, see for example Foong et al. (2021) in the small-data regime.",
    "As explained in Section 1.4, empirical PAC-Bayes bounds are very useful as they provide a numerical certificate for randomized estimators or aggregated predictors.",
